Description: Everyone likes a funnyman! With the power of comedy everyone will want to talk to you!
Your life is so tragic! People online are sure to sympathize and give you all the support you could want!
Makeup tutorials and fancy cars! When you pop up on someone's feed you're sure to earn their loyalty!
Unfazed and cynical. Your professional attitude is sure to earn you respect from every nihilist you come across!
Hiding may not be great at drawing attention, but you'll be even more special to the ones you choose to talk too!
